  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d659aa9d-a9ff-4046-8f9b-106cadd76e8c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a747b353-a4b2-48f9-a6e7-bacb1916d98d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f89d57a9-e0bc-4fce-b635-655276ab1c93\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>갤러리 홍보용 인쇄물 : 엽서</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2985ed04-ac53-4150-86c7-b4069d15a7a2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-0d497d8d-0f2b-4d05-85c3-00b24189e1f0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-355a51db-772e-4e75-9fab-f7e349654ff5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">2019년에 저를 주축으로 하여 5개 회사가 갤러리 인쇄물의 홍보와 매출을 목표로 갤러리인사이트라는 회사를 설립하였습니다. 약 3년간 꾸준히 활동였으며 5개 회사는 각자의 길로 분산되어 현재 활발히 인쇄 영업중에 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-7d7918af-91bb-4a64-86b3-b8aa6d4dce72\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-66380f92-5402-48b1-8c97-c356f7017540\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-311bd555-8af4-48ad-9647-9573c5034966\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4fd004ab-3fa8-4a70-a051-f1a604c79c84\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a9c36d9-0f06-4cc9-9ebb-0f65b91519c7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d724ef72-7a8d-4486-b6da-f82ceb1b548b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c9fa0982-7cde-4478-a7c4-3b8549e4cd8a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">엽서는 다음과 같은 사양으로 진행하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b937b47f-d714-4a72-bb2e-081d96c126ac\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ef8d4c9c-02f1-4b4c-9542-7d2a3f0b27ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a9f16ec2-09f4-47f1-9617-7b3296fbed59\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-35062120-efc0-42ab-b3c6-93d5bebb8339\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-73f38597-bd45-4a33-8b6d-6d5cedfcc175\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e3e6be64-a0fa-4a1b-9c85-6be46d518030\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">원고 : 선방 제공 또는 (주)파파스컴퍼니 디자인 작업, 엽서는 그 형태상 간단한 디자인으로 제작이 됩니다. 이 비용은 협의에 따라 무료로 제작될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-98c67abc-f017-4513-9650-af2d36581eab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2c95cfc0-ec38-4b79-b7ef-b9b87a39a96a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-1c66d1ac-545b-4130-9772-2e447a365302\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7be810e8-747b-47f9-b663-422fe1db8063\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">전면에는 본인 전시의 사진을 이미지로 통상 넣고 후면에는 간단한 전시회 정보와 연락처 정보만을 간단히 넣는 것을 기본으로 합니다. 이 부분의 디자인은 수량이나 결제금액에 따라 무료로 진행되고 있으며 인쇄물을 의뢰제작하시면 별도로 이미지로 전달할 수 있는 png파일을 별도로 제작하여 공급할 수도 있습니다. (디자인 주문시 선택사항)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-3e07bfa5-e897-4653-8d5d-27521f4ed3a1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9364a6a6-ef6b-4bf2-a05a-500614630778\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1fade178-0a98-4545-a8c5-e65ea9b8a0d4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5583ed1e-2657-4560-8056-f355fd77c116\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-b9755314-7ed6-4543-a5ac-fa607ef9fc04\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-62c2073a-f367-4dd8-af27-ec245e9cfdde\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이런 류의 배너형이나 카톡으로 보낼 수 있는 이미지를 제작하여 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e333253b-d834-4e61-bf0a-cbc87b00bd4c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d8a08081-5c02-480f-8837-7ed59a61f672\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-ac9f8bde-abef-4fae-acbd-8fb5ca97e8ab\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-66733b96-4be5-4c84-b790-71c7f8f99395\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-df29498c-d4a7-487a-950b-d76804fff764\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9eec2257-2362-4395-88ce-87dd9da6f5cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69ad82b3-b35b-4239-b7c5-2aa1a07e289a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f430f8c3-9ae2-448e-baa8-7fa4437df87c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-94f462eb-1a04-45d3-b5cb-1b3dd556ca5a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-97c9ea60-0c62-4d08-9b7d-39b087f764f0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">랑데뷰 울트라화이트 240g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-889539ff-f1fd-432d-b213-d4ea9530865e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-494322e3-e72a-4a4e-9937-c61cec0b48ce\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">모조지 백색 260g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-61307879-77b4-437f-b7a9-5b16bab082a2\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-794cda26-134b-4e77-80ed-a1f4df54fb92\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">스노우지 백색 250g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9b46c5c6-f06b-4492-b3c3-f9787e8055cb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c25befd5-dd9e-46fe-85af-1bcee9169f0a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-004a2549-e2e7-44ce-95fa-27cd10482861\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d5a17da9-38c3-488f-9a19-d25100841783\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">거의 대부분 하얀색의 백색 종이를 선호하십니다. 깔끔한 작품을 표현하는데 방해되는 종이는 가급적 피하고 있습니다. 이 3가지 종이 이외에도 다양한 종이로 제작될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5bc6b21b-f139-4301-8222-17391b97406b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-55cc801d-5b4e-494f-95d4-b9d427244661\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd58e3ce-680a-463e-a480-9f46b6804f95\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3eaa4d33-3a98-490d-a84c-ca9100f8f3bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-82b62e30-cda6-42da-ac45-857750d2fa55\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1915efa4-97c3-4d18-80ee-a079244a41cc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-da7e82e0-f106-47b5-9501-1cbd39ecbbf1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-95f1b224-5796-4a8b-bee0-6621f6a68de0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본사이즈 A5 150mm × 210mm </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-050967fa-514e-4386-a1f7-742de190ab51\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-df651768-db06-41db-82fb-905df3a8981b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본사이즈 B6 120mm × 170mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cfe8dbd4-00e8-4298-aaae-1438ca8c455b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b587700b-f1cf-401d-9c44-3e6983ca1a8e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b56afd32-f346-406f-8c04-0c1d45ec1f0d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-98e427d3-a7eb-46e7-9a25-21ca6be00cd8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2868ef0c-4fb7-4459-a653-7d850d32f908\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">위의 두가지 기본사이즈를 제일 많이 사용합니다. 주문의 80% 이상을 차지합니다. 이외의 사이즈는 단가나 기타부분으로 문의주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-9462c4f6-d43b-45d2-9136-61afa2fb0dee\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-366c492c-9682-4500-a915-b403a0f3ee86\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-844ea35f-2781-43c1-875d-7e31566adaa3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ab0fd739-2625-4253-914c-af4f716f6eee\" sty