n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4533591f-a877-433b-a866-1df2d180a8b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-29a32602-e2d1-4028-a30b-f38015ad7b67\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3a4964ef-57e6-4332-bb1c-da15c63725cf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본적인 세트는 엽서, 2/3단 리플렛, 명함입니다. 갤러리 전시시 사용하는 인쇄물로서 기본전시에 고객에게 나눠주는 엽서를 시작으로 작가의 홍보나 작품해설이 들어가는 리플렛, 그리고 현장에서 막 배포하는 명함등을 기본세트로 주문을 많이 하십니다. 또한 작품에 붙이는 캡션도 제작중에 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7ebdc936-2e1c-421e-a435-7cf0f50590b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1e0ddc1-7534-4fb4-9f35-fb26ea020224\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a7a4b6a-cf10-4708-b22d-c4032cbc9595\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2fd889c8-3064-4c8c-b7e6-e97d9dc2e236\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">캡션은 작품에 붙이는 투명한 인쇄물을 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-99a96cad-4499-4b98-8d53-c54eb1f40874\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d5d46775-499a-43d3-8732-0da5fd2d6f21\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7366e6e6-a4d6-4c72-9127-600b1c04fb47\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bf2d794c-88c4-42f2-a828-ac6cd426289e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5a3cf3c9-ec36-4c98-9b90-51118e582116\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-92504871-b407-492b-8f5e-ccf8aecd2388\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이나 사이즈 수량은 자유롭게 선택이 가능합니다. 다만 기본적인 사양이 벗어날 경우 단가에 영향을 미칠 수 있습니다. 이 부분은 반드시 문의를 주시고 판단하시기를 권장드립니다. 기본적인 사양은 위의 예시를 통해 알려드렸습니다. 갤러리는 일단 전시와 홍보에 치중하고 인쇄물 제작은 믿고 맡길 수 있는 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하여 주십시요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-48133802-170d-45ba-bb9c-5c596cdb128c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a9816bc2-eb72-4c22-b897-66beb8c75df7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7da89331-7eec-41f4-8e78-56bc4f1b666d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8470148c-c572-4b4c-bbf0-0b59c8a03fe4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-377bb97e-0c60-4949-8562-eb7536360e89\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ae71b8bf-07f9-4a6e-b4f6-b728ae586575\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">파트 2에서 더 디테일한 내용을 설명드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ff45dcbc-1161-4d3e-9642-be8f9ba42e29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c59419db-dc61-4d3e-8353-d98a616c4933\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222934239556/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c17fbcf0-f4d4-430a-b6ed-399e8d41d08d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e46af12f-eeeb-4405-b16d-7151cd94c058\" style=\"\">디자인 템플릿 예시</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8340374c-18ed-48ee-a07f-2aaf5eb7e422\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}